    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_A0F095A0-093A-0135-D150-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If a user has been manually added to a course but has not yet accepted the course invitation after a period of time, you can resend the course invitation. You must allow at least 24 hours before resending a course invitation.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>Users are not sent a course invitation until the course participation start date. (The start date is commonly the term date, unless the term is being overridden by a specific course or section participation date in Course Settings.) Additionally, courses must be published for students to receive course invitations. </p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_people" data-step-uuid="EEA0DE6A-3D51-41A9-9C73-1474BFA353F1">
