      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="resend_individual_invitation" data-step-uuid="DE00D957-2ED5-43B0-B66C-57CA16A86613">
    <h2 id="resend_individual_invitation" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Resend Individual Invitation</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/250/714/original/430635cf-0aaa-4770-9c16-017df91fba0b.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/250/714/medium/430635cf-0aaa-4770-9c16-017df91fba0b.png" srcset="" alt="Resend Individual Invitation" height="256" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_A0F21570-093A-0135-D156-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To resend an invitation, locate the user's name and click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1], then select the <strong>Resend Invitation </strong>link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="resend_all_invitations" data-step-uuid="08525954-7561-4c22-8bb5-f1b96ac16278">
    <h2 id="resend_all_invitations" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Resend All Invitations</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/250/709/original/42261630-8d64-424b-910b-2d232d4eadee.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/250/709/medium/42261630-8d64-424b-910b-2d232d4eadee.png" srcset="" alt="Resend All Invitations" height="260" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_A0F2CF40-093A-0135-D158-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To resend all pending invitations, click the <strong>Resend </strong>link.</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> The <strong>Resend</strong> link does not display until at least 24 hours after a user received the course invitation.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
